title: VA - Disco Vaults 2 (A Slide Under The Strobe Light) (2002)@flac
description:
Warner Music of Greece sent us another package with their newly released volume 2 of their highly regarded Disco Vault series. 
They've taken selections from Warner, Atlantic, Elektra, WMOT and Fantasy Records to bring you hard-to-find Disco classics on two beautifully packaged CDs. Includes liner notes with scans of the original vinyl from which they were taken.

Please note that this is a limited release Greek import and a very difficult to obtain. (discomusic.com)
